'''星光'''是[[恆星|恆星]]發射的[[光|光]]<ref name=krob/>，它通常是指在[[地球|地球]][[晚上|夜間]]來自恆星[[可見光譜|可見光]]的[[電磁輻射|電磁輻射]]；在[[白天|白天]]，除了[[太陽|太陽]]之外其它天體的星光也可以觀測得到。

[[陽光|陽光]]這個術語是用在白天看見來自太陽的星光。在夜晚，[[反照率|反照率]]是描述來自太陽系的其它天體，包括[[月光|月光]]，反射的陽光。

通過望遠鏡觀察和測量星光，是[[天文學|天文學]]許多領域的基礎<ref name=mac>{{cite book |url=http://books.google.com/books?id=O80YAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA191&dq=Starlight+astronomy&hl=en&ei=qQWkTLevG4O8lQfc5-ySDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CDIQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false |first=Hector |last=Macpherson |title=The romance of modern astronomy |year=1911 |page=191 |access-date=2014-02-28 |archive-date=2020-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200125052901/https://books.google.com/books?id=O80YAAAAYAAJ&pg=PA191&dq=Starlight+astronomy&hl=en&ei=qQWkTLevG4O8lQfc5-ySDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CDIQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref>，包括光度法和恆星光譜<ref name=hearn/>。星光也是許多[[個人經驗|個人經驗]]和人類[[文化|文化]]中值得注意的，影響各種各樣的發展，包括詩歌<ref name=skinner>[http://books.google.com/books?id=Fag_AAAAYAAJ&pg=PA102&dq=Starlight+composition&hl=en&ei=Ol8GTamcIcSqlAeNhaWXCA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CDgQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q&f=false Wells Hawks Skinner - ''Studies in literature and composition for high schools, normal schools, and ...'' (1897) - Page 102] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=Fag_AAAAYAAJ&pg=PA102&dq=Starlight+composition&hl=en&ei=Ol8GTamcIcSqlAeNhaWXCA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CDgQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q&f=false |date=20140628162154 }} (Google eBook link)</ref>、天文學<ref name=mac/>、和軍事行動<ref name=mort>[http://books.google.com/books?id=HNgDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA79&dq=Starlight+army&hl=en&ei=AWgGTfuLC4GClAePtf3OCQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CCoQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=Starlight%20army&f=false Popular Mechanics - Jan 1969 - "How the Army Learned to See in the Dark" by Mort Schultz] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=HNgDAAAAMBAJ&pg=PA79&dq=Starlight+army&hl=en&ei=AWgGTfuLC4GClAePtf3OCQ&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CCoQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=Starlight%20army&f=false |date=20140628162413 }} (Google Books link)</ref>。

美國軍方在1950年代花費數以百萬計的美元，發展出[[夜視鏡|星光夜視鏡]]，可以放大星光、被雲遮蔽的月光和來自植物的螢光，達到50,000倍，讓人可以在夜晚看得見<ref name=mort/>。相較之前發射紅外線的系統，像是''狙擊鏡''，它是一種無源系統，不需要額外的發射光源來觀看<ref name=mort/>。

在宇宙中的星光顏色平均是陰暗的黃白色，已被命名為[[宇宙拿鐵|宇宙拿鐵]]。
 
星光光譜學，恆星光譜的調查，最早在1814年由[[約瑟夫·弗勞恩霍夫|約瑟夫·弗勞恩霍夫]]開創<ref name=hearn>[http://books.google.com/books?id=iCs4AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA51&dq=Starlight+spectrum&hl=en&ei=OGIGTfL_BIH-8Aag9tjwDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCMQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Starlight%20spectrum&f=false  J. B. Hearnshaw - ''The analysis of starlight: one hundred and fifty years of astronomical spectroscopy '' (1990) - Page 51] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=iCs4AAAAIAAJ&pg=PA51&dq=Starlight+spectrum&hl=en&ei=OGIGTfL_BIH-8Aag9tjwDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCMQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Starlight%20spectrum&f=false |date=20140628162402 }} (Google Books link)</ref>。星光可以被分類為三種主要的光譜類型：連續譜、發射譜、和吸收譜<ref name=krob>[http://books.google.com/books?id=wkIOzagyQmAC&pg=PA38&dq=Starlight+spectrum&hl=en&ei=OGIGTfL_BIH-8Aag9tjwDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CDIQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Starlight%20spectrum&f=false Keith Robinson - ''Starlight: An Introduction to Stellar Physics for Amateurs'' (2009) - Page 38-40] {{Wayback|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=wkIOzagyQmAC&pg=PA38&dq=Starlight+spectrum&hl=en&ei=OGIGTfL_BIH-8Aag9tjwDA&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CDIQ6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Starlight%20spectrum&f=false |date=20140628162001 }} (Google Books Link)</ref>。

